	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Dec 3rd 7:06 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you think there are no good 1hb weaps, then you're sorely mistaken. The MoSS(Mace of the Shadowed Soul 19/29 INT+10) is a very good 1hb weapon. A melee class should train in every combat skill like this so they can be well rounded. It also can be a lot easier to shop for yurself because you won't have to limit yurself to any type of skill. I trained my Sk in 1hs 2hs Piercing and now im on 1hb with a MoSS. I'm really lucky to have done this because i can shop a lot easier for my SK. As far as that guy who hates evrything...chill. Druids aren't all bad. In fact, i know plenty of druids who are nicer people than me...and im a pretty nice person. About the halflings...don't insult the people playing the characters...you don't know them personally so don't trash them. <br><br>Asaku Dragonslayer 25 Shadow Knight<br>Krystaleyes Fallenstar 23 Shaman<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
